# isync / mbsync example
# https://isync.sourceforge.io/
#
# Place at ~/.mbsyncrc

IMAPAccount personal
Host imap.example.com
User you@example.com
PassCmd "+kpget 'Email/personal'"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

MaildirStore personal-local
Path ~/Maildir/personal/
Inbox ~/Maildir/personal/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel personal
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
